            .paragraph
                p United Porte is a manufacturer and supplier of doors, windows, and furniture in the USA. The main task was to update the website design with a focus on enhancing product customization. Now, users can not only change the size and color of selected items but also adjust additional parameters such as glass type, locks, hinges, and more.
                p In addition to introducing new functionality, the redesign involved optimizing all pages of the online store to improve the user experience and increase conversion rates.
