        .case_text 
            p Previously, customers had to choose doors from a general category, but if a specific detail, such as the lock mechanism or hinges, didn’t fit, they had to search for another model in the overall list. This significantly complicated the user flow and made the selection process less convenient.
            p Therefore, a new feature has been added to the product page, allowing customers to customize doors by changing the hinges, glass type, lock type and design, as well as the color and material of the door. Now, buyers can easily adjust the doors to match their interior design and personal.

